create unique synergies between them. From a sniper tower firing every 0.2 seconds radioactive projectiles, to a rocket tower firing 4 rockets at once with a disc saw, everything is possible !<br>Global Upgrade are applied to the terrain or your loadout.<br>Some loadouts even have some unique global upgrades ! <br>It's up to you to discover them !<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481000/extras/0c55c8b6f61ba00c72771a0a5df6ce08.poster.avif?t=1725971559\" width=638 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481000/extras/0c55c8b6f61ba00c72771a0a5df6ce08.webm?t=1725971559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481000/extras/0c55c8b6f61ba00c72771a0a5df6ce08.mp4?t=1725971559\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >progression:</h2>With each run or achievement you complete, you will be able to buy new content: tower upgrades, global upgrades, and even loadouts!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481000/extras/d2fab59611bf44d1bf218358d7e8fac3.poster.avif?t=1725971559\" width=638 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481000/extras/d2fab59611bf44d1bf218358d7e8fac3.webm?t=1725971559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481000/extras/d2fab59611bf44d1bf218358d7e8fac3.mp4?t=1725971559\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
